whole_object: Looks like even the trees are branching out into new parking spaces nowadays!
single_object:
- Tree: "I'm quite poplar in this neighborhood, branching out to make new friends!"
- Parking meter: "Just standing here, collecting change, like a piggy bank with a better view."
- Cars: "Always in a race to nowhere, they're tired of the daily commute!"
- Building: "I've got many stories, but I'll save the tall tales for later."
- Traffic cone: "I'm the life of the party, always cone-tributing to street safety!"
- Sidewalk: "I provide support to everyone, but nobody ever takes me out for a walk."
multi_object:

- "The tree was feeling a bit shady, especially with that parking meter always counting its leaves!"
